_sText:
Arches by Terry Taylor
----------------------

Firstly, I'd like to point out that this is my first map so, any constructive critisism is
welcome!

This is a shootout map for CS:S, no hostages or bombs, just kill the enemy to win.
Has space for 9 per team, If you need more spaces, drop me an e-mail.

and now that i've worked out how to set the buy zones, it makes quite an interesting map

I've deliberately put the crates in the tunnel to stop snipers taking out the whole team.

Any comments for me please direct them to TaylorT063@aol.com

Tel
